markdownRemark.html: The resort is located in El Rompido, a picturesque fishing village on the west coast of Huelva. The two golf courses (north and south) are lovely and challenging. There is a Spa and gym onsite. The pro shop has plenty of choice for men and women. There are large practice areas and driving ranges available.
